    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis of the comprehensive multi-study provenance chain anchored to the FDA benchmark dataset and the shear-stress sub-model synthesis node, which consolidates three decades of hemolysis literature. The Monte Carlo UQ envelope was judged sufficient to bound clinical risk at the accepted operating envelope. Residual gaps in model form and discretization error are acknowledged and will be addressed in a follow-on assessment cycle.",
